api-reference/async_tagging.title: Attribute Extraction - Asynchronous
api-reference/async_tagging.description: This API returns AI powered product tags asynchronously. We also support sending back responses to a client hosted callback URL when the response is ready.

api-reference/tagging_feedback.title: Attribute Extraction - Feedback
api-reference/tagging_feedback.description: This API accepts feedback on attributes for any given mad_id.
